abstract: Moroccan security forces arrest hundreds of African migrants in country's north in attempt to keep them from crossing illegally into Spain.
lead_paragraph: Moroccan security forces raided a mountain camp and arrested hundreds of migrants in the country illegally, officials said Wednesday.

headline.main: Morocco: Migrants’ Camp Cleared Out in Crackdown
